1
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:39,106
[The Age of Awakening]

2
00:01:39,130 --> 00:01:42,216
[Episode Two]

3
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,656
Brothers have to go to work now.

4
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:44,896
I can't play with you this time.

5
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,456
Next time?

6
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,456
Let's go.

7
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:49,440
Goodbye Aunt.

8
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:53,103
Wait a minute. Wait a minute.

9
00:01:53,127 --> 00:01:54,416
Come.

10
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:55,136
Take all the buns.

11
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:56,976
Brother, you promised to give me a grasshopper!

12
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:59,016
I'll keep my promise!

13
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,282
Come home if you need to.

14
00:02:00,282 --> 00:02:02,286
Thank you Aunt.

15
00:02:21,972 --> 00:02:23,896
{\an8}[Songshan Road, French Concession, Shanghai]

16
00:02:23,896 --> 00:02:25,807
{\an8}[Songshan Road, French Concession, Shanghai]
Pear paste pastries... sweet and savoury,

17
00:02:25,807 --> 00:02:26,931
{\an8}[Songshan Road, French Concession, Shanghai]
a mouthful of delight!

18
00:02:26,931 --> 00:02:28,177
a mouthful of delight!

19
00:02:28,201 --> 00:02:29,485
The song goes:

20
00:02:29,485 --> 00:02:30,681
{\an8}[Chen Henian, youngest son of Chen Duxiu]

21
00:02:29,485 --> 00:02:31,773
Xiao Fangqing in the Pearl Tower

22
00:02:31,797 --> 00:02:33,120
is so happy to meet

23
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,723
Xiao Qingqing in "The Legend of the White Snake".

24
00:02:34,723 --> 00:02:37,098
Xiao Fangqing

25
00:02:37,122 --> 00:02:39,060
is so happy

26
00:02:39,084 --> 00:02:43,048
to the movies with her.

27
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:53,920
Hey! Selling pear pastries!

28
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,520
Good, stop!

29
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:02,760
Mr Menzou is here!

30
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:07,586
{\an8}[Wang Mengzou, Manager of Yadong Library]

31
00:03:07,610 --> 00:03:08,776
Menzou!

32
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,376
Junman!

33
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,816
I've brought you Zhong Fu back from the dock!

34
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,976
Where?

35
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,256
At the back!

36
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,800
Look!

37
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:25,016
Zimei! Henian! Look who's back!

38
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:27,520
It's Dad! Call Dad!

39
00:03:31,165 --> 00:03:34,880
{\an8}[Chen Duxiu, styled Zhong Fu, famous revolutionary]

40
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,520
Why don't you have an umbrella?

41
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:04,800
Zimei! Henian!

42
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,856
Qiaonian? Yannian? Where are they?

43
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:15,496
Let's go home first.

44
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,776
Okay, go, go, go.

45
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,656
Let's go home!

46
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,680
Thank you, Menzou.

47
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:24,400
Go, go, go!

48
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,576
What are you doing?

49
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,960
What are you doing out in the rain?

50
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:58,160
Tasting the Jiangnan rain.

51
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:02,176
Quick, quick, quick!

52
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:04,256
Were you that stupid in Japan?

53
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,936
Look at the rain on you!

54
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:07,336
There's raindrops all over!

55
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,320
What's a drop of rain?

56
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,256
When I was in Japan,

57
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:13,480
I was covered in lice.

58
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:16,256
Once.

59
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:20,096
Then Zhang Shizhao asked me to edit an issue.

60
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:22,056
I locked myself in my room,

61
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,976
I didn't leave the house for half a month.

62
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,616
Then the article was finished.

63
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,816
I went out,

64
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:29,096
Yi Baisha looked at me and said:

65
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:31,336
What are those spots on your body?

66
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,536
I looked down and it was all...

67
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:36,040
Don't say, don't say, don't say.

68
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,136
Mr Chen.

69
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:47,240
You've suffered.

70
00:05:52,016 --> 00:05:53,803
Come. Sit.

71
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:58,160
Sit with me and listen to the rain for a while.

72
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:05,976
There is no revolution without suffering,

73
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:09,496
but I brought this misery upon myself.

74
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:12,856
I like to... I like to enjoy it.

75
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:16,536
It's just that... I got you into trouble.

76
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,376
You're a talented student from Beijing Normal University,

77
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:20,720
suffering with me.

78
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,720
I'm sorry.

79
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:24,936
As long as the family can be together,

80
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:27,376
whatever the suffering and hardship,

81
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:29,400
I'm not afraid.

82
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:35,016
It's just that Yannian and Qiaonian don't want to go home.

83
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:37,480
I don't feel well.

84
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:39,920
Zhong Fu.

85
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:43,416
Why don't you go and get the two children tomorrow

86
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:45,336
and bring them home?

87
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,816
Don't let them roam around outside.

88
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:49,280
I'm not going to pick them up.

89
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:53,040
These two boys have a lot of backbone.

90
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:57,960
It's good to go out and make your own living.

91
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:00,496
Yannian and Qiaonian

92
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:03,176
are two good boys with big ambitions.

93
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:05,216
After the May 9th National Disgrace,

94
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,936
they both came to Shanghai to study.

95
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,656
Seeing our family's difficulties,

96
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,736
they had brought from the countryside

97
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:11,256
100 silver yuan for tuition

98
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,696
and gave it to me.

99
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,696
They went out to work on their own.

100
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,736
I tried to give it back to them

101
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:17,376
but they wouldn't listen.

102
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:20,000
You said Shanghai docks are so rough.

103
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:24,080
What would happen if something happened to them?

104
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,440
Zhong Fu.

105
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:28,016
I'm begging you.

106
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:30,560
You go and bring them both home.

107
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,896
Junman.

108
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:35,160
When I was abroad,

109
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:38,696
I heard a song from Europe

110
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,616
called "The Internationale".

111
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:43,896
Although the lyrics have not been translated into Chinese,

112
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,376
there are a few lines in it

113
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:47,416
I was very impressed by.

114
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,696
The idea is

115
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:51,160
there is no saviour

116
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:54,080
or there is no fairy god.

117
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:57,680
To create happiness for all

118
00:07:57,800 --> 00:08:00,440
is up to us.

119
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:03,296
Well sung... well said.

120
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:06,520
From large countries to small individuals,

121
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:09,741
one should forge their own destiny.

122
00:08:09,765 --> 00:08:10,656
Trusting your life

123
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,496
to your father and family.

124
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:14,176
You can't rely on that.

125
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:17,336
So, what is the job of the father?

126
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:19,237
Where has your duty as a father gone?

127
00:08:19,237 --> 00:08:21,216
It is my duty

128
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:23,296
to let them know

129
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:25,216
how to be live up to

130
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:29,160
the social and historical responsibilities of this country.

131
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,976
In these troubled times,

132
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,696
to be a son of I, Chen Duxiu,

133
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:37,616
one must first work hard on one's heart and soul.

134
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:39,656
Starve the body and the skin, but not the soul.

135
00:08:39,680 --> 00:08:40,976
Act in accordance with the law,

136
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,696
so your heart is willing

137
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,576
to endure what it once could not.

138
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:47,576
You are a thinker against the ways of Confucius and Mencius.

139
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:49,176
Why did you make a statement

140
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,496
out of Mencius' quotes?

141
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:52,816
Yuan Shikai wants to make Confucianism the state religion,

142
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,376
of course I want to oppose it.

143
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,976
But make no mistake,

144
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:56,976
I am against

145
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,976
the three principles of Confucianism that are poisoning the people.

146
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:03,600
Neither Confucius nor Mencius.

147
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:08,000
All right, all right, I can't talk you out of it.

148
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:10,976
Step inside.

149
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:13,280
It's cold.

150
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,520
Let's go.

151
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:23,061
{\an8}[Yadong Library]

152
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,640
Brother.

153
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,416
That thing, put it in the jar.

154
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,856
Is it fine?

155
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:39,720
It's fine.

156
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:43,656
You're all set, right?

157
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:44,976
There is no point in playing chess. Put it back.

158
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,920
Ready to go Huangshan, Maofeng?

159
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:50,536
Zhong Fu!

160
00:09:50,536 --> 00:09:51,659
Brother Zhong Fu!

161
00:09:51,683 --> 00:09:52,000
Zhong Fu!

162
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:52,536
Put it here.

163
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:53,536
Come on, come on, we're waiting for you.

164
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:54,056
Zhong Fu, ladies and gentlemen!

165
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:54,896
Everyone's here!

166
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:57,360
Brother Zhong Fu, we're all waiting for you!

167
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,616
Zishou.

168
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,360
Zipei.

169
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,740
{\an8}[Yi Baisha, styled Yue Cun, scholar of the New Culture movement]

170
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:02,923
Zhong Fu.

171
00:10:02,923 --> 00:10:04,718
Baisha.

172
00:10:05,249 --> 00:10:05,716
Zhong Fu.

173
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,240
Yongcheng.

174
00:10:07,463 --> 00:10:09,800
{\an8}[Zou Yongcheng, styled Qi Zhi]

175
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:10,096
Since we left the boat, I've missed you.

176
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,960
Greetings, gentlemen.

177
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:13,976
Come on, you're barging in.

178
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,816
Go and meet us at the front!

179
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:18,176
No, I'm not going to meet him.

180
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:20,736
Why is this child so stubborn?

181
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:23,176
You tell me, he's still your old man,

182
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:25,336
then the bones are still attached to the tendons.

183
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:27,016
Where did all the hate come from?

184
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:28,136
I don't have a grudge against him,

185
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:29,776
but I just don't go to see him.

186
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:31,816
Same temper as your father.

187
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,376
I'm sure of it.

188
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:36,160
I can't get it back with nine oxen.

189
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,536
The fire is good.

190
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:39,056
Why are you, Wang Menzou,

191
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:41,016
so stingy?

192
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:42,376
I'm invited to dinner,

193
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:44,336
not at a restaurant, but at a home.

194
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:46,240
How much money do you save?

195
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,416
He said it! I do save money.

196
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,576
What would you like to eat?

197
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:51,176
I prepared it all yesterday.

198
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:54,376
The cook was also taken from Zishou's house.

199
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:56,536
I didn't spend any mony on this.

200
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:57,856
I can attest.

201
00:10:57,880 --> 00:11:00,016
What Menzou said is true in every sense of the word.

202
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,136
{\an8}[Chen Zishou, owner of Qunyi Book Club]
Our family cook

203
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:03,160
{\an8}[Chen Zishou, owner of Qunyi Book Club]
was dragged here by him.

204
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:06,376
Zhong Fu, I'm borrowing the cook's skills.

205
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:08,136
You should also write us a couple of words.

206
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,336
To each his own.

207
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,256
He gave me a reception

208
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:11,456
by borrowing the cook from you.

209
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,696
He should be grateful to you.

210
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,560
What's it to do with me?

211
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,136
Me!

212
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:18,096
Zhong Fu, who is the stingy one?

213
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:19,776
Of course, he's stingy one!

214
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:22,936
And the famous Yadong Library

215
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,816
has always been housed in this alley.

216
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:26,296
I've tried so many times to get him to move out

217
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,336
but he won't listen!

218
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:29,176
It's easy to move out!

219
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:30,096
Wang Mengzou, I tell you,

220
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:32,416
we are doing great things with a bang.

221
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,296
If you want to die,

222
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,616
just cower in the alleyway.

223
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:35,656
If you want to live,

224
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:36,776
you have to move out of the alleyway

225
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,456
and onto the main road.

226
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,336
All right, all right.

227
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,696
You're standing around talking,

228
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,096
then sit down and talk.

229
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,720
Everyone sit down.

230
00:11:44,575 --> 00:11:46,053
Sit down, sit down.

231
00:11:46,077 --> 00:11:46,724
{\an8}[Chen Qiaonian, second son of Chen Duxiu]
Qiaonian.

232
00:11:46,724 --> 00:11:47,199
{\an8}[Chen Qiaonian, second son of Chen Duxiu]

233
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,896
{\an8}[Chen Qiaonian, second son of Chen Duxiu]
You're too young to hold a grudge.

234
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:51,936
This is a lotus leaf and yellow beef feet dish.

235
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,696
Serve it to your father.

236
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,816
Meet him.

237
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,656
Give him a surprise.

238
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:58,056
OK, I'll send him up later

239
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,216
and surprise him.

240
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,200
{\an8}[Chen Yannian, eldest son of Chen Duxiu]
That's right!

241
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:02,016
{\an8}[Chen Yannian, eldest son of Chen Duxiu]

242
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:04,576
Today, everyone invited to

243
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,416
firstly

244
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:08,616
celebrate Zhong Fu's return to the country.

245
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:09,896
That's the second.

246
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:12,456
Since the failure of the Second Revolution,

247
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:14,416
We revolutionaries

248
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:16,616
have been scattered to the winds.

249
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:19,456
We went our separate ways and hid into hiding.

250
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:21,656
Some died, some were wounded.

251
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:24,256
Today, having us all here together

252
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:26,016
after the disaster

253
00:12:26,040 --> 00:12:27,576
is not easy.

254
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,336
The situation now

255
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:31,536
is that European powers are at war.

256
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:33,136
Originally it was our country's

257
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:35,816
time to take a break.

258
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,776
But what about the Japanese?

259
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:38,454
They took advantage of the situation,

260
00:12:38,478 --> 00:12:39,160
by proposing

261
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:42,296
the Twenty-One Demands of powers in Shandong.

262
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,376
That Yuan Shikai,

263
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:46,896
betrayed the country with the National Humiliation of May 9th.

264
00:12:46,920 --> 00:12:49,600
A disgrace. It is truly a disgrace.

265
00:12:46,920 --> 00:12:49,543
{\an8}[Chen Zipei, Owner of Qunyi Book Club]

266
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:52,416
And now the entire country is seething,

267
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,936
protesting.

268
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:56,336
At this time, what should we do?

269
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,576
Observe with a critical eye?

270
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:59,976
Be docile subjects? Be a conquered people?

271
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,216
Never.

272
