00:23:30,840 --> 00:23:33,336
What's... what's going on here?

552
00:23:33,360 --> 00:23:35,320
I don't know!

553
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:38,456
Mr. Chen, don't be angry. Mrs. Chen, don't be angry.

554
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:40,216
It's all my fault. My fault!

555
00:23:40,240 --> 00:23:42,720
Sister-in-law, it's not your fault.

556
00:23:43,320 --> 00:23:44,096
Qiaonian.

557
00:23:44,120 --> 00:23:45,960
What's going on?

558
00:23:46,280 --> 00:23:48,656
You shouldn't be the only one who did it.

559
00:23:48,680 --> 00:23:49,976
Where are your associates?

560
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:51,215
Bring him here.

561
00:23:51,239 --> 00:23:54,896
Chen Yannian, come out!

562
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:05,696
I'm the mastermind of this.

563
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:06,976
Take it out on me if you're angry.

564
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:08,856
Yannian, how old are you?

565
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:10,216
Are you still a child?

566
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:11,216
You are an adult!

567
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:13,536
How could you do such a ridiculous thing?

568
00:24:13,560 --> 00:24:15,468
Even if you have a problem with your old man,

569
00:24:15,492 --> 00:24:16,640
you can't treat him like this!

570
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:19,136
Do you know what you call this?

571
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:20,976
This is called treason!

572
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:23,096
This would be frowned upon in our home town!

573
00:24:23,120 --> 00:24:25,240
Heaven condemns you!

574
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:31,536
Sorry, Uncle Wang, Aunt Wang.

575
00:24:31,560 --> 00:24:33,136
I've put you in a difficult position.

576
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:34,296
I do this today,

577
00:24:34,320 --> 00:24:35,616
not because of him, Chen Duxiu,

578
00:24:35,640 --> 00:24:38,216
who didn't take enough care of my mother and us two brothers.

579
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:39,176
In Anqing,

580
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,776
we were not rich.

581
00:24:40,800 --> 00:24:42,336
But at least the family has some property,

582
00:24:42,360 --> 00:24:44,816
enough for our family to live on.

583
00:24:44,840 --> 00:24:46,296
Since he doesn't care about us,

584
00:24:46,320 --> 00:24:47,816
we won't beg him again.

585
00:24:47,840 --> 00:24:49,576
We're doing this today

586
00:24:49,600 --> 00:24:51,616
for the sake of our suffering family

587
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:52,536
and for

588
00:24:52,560 --> 00:24:54,376
our cousin Chen Yongnian, who has been tortured because of him,

589
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:56,920
to teach him a lesson.

590
00:24:57,760 --> 00:24:59,736
To speak of treason,

591
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:01,576
Chen Duxiu is the one who is really

592
00:25:01,600 --> 00:25:03,456
a treacherous hypocrite.

593
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:05,416
Yannian, you're going too far!

594
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:06,536
Don't talk about your father like that!

595
00:25:06,560 --> 00:25:07,496
You shut up!

596
00:25:07,520 --> 00:25:08,936
Let him speak.

597
00:25:08,960 --> 00:25:10,096
Alright.

598
00:25:10,120 --> 00:25:11,976
Today, in front of all my uncles and aunts,

599
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:14,336
I'm going to reveal the shame of our Chen family.

600
00:25:14,360 --> 00:25:16,136
Everyone please judge.

601
00:25:16,160 --> 00:25:17,456
Last autumn,

602
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:19,456
after the failure of the Second Revolution in Anqing,

603
00:25:19,480 --> 00:25:22,133
Chen Duxiu himself abandons his family and flees,

604
00:25:22,157 --> 00:25:23,736
knowing the danger,

605
00:25:23,760 --> 00:25:25,216
but still left his sick grandmother

606
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:27,696
and our mother and son behind.

607
00:25:27,720 --> 00:25:30,416
Ni Xichong sent his men to raid our house.

608
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:32,256
My sister, Yuying, sacrificed her life to block the front hall

609
00:25:32,280 --> 00:25:35,896
covering me and Qiaonian to jump out of the window.

610
00:25:35,920 --> 00:25:37,256
Cousin Chen Yongnian

611
00:25:37,280 --> 00:25:39,016
who protected his younger brother Chen Zhannian

612
00:25:39,040 --> 00:25:40,976
was arrested for pretending to be me,

613
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:43,896
and was tortured to death.

614
00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:47,216
Grandfather, who died after a long illness, was still at home

615
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:50,240
Grandmother is bedridden.

616
00:25:50,424 --> 00:25:52,296
The family rushed to Shanghai

617
00:25:52,320 --> 00:25:53,616
to find Chen Duxiu,

618
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:56,856
asking him to return for his father's funeral.

619
00:25:56,880 --> 00:25:58,736
But he was greedy for life and death.

620
00:25:58,760 --> 00:26:00,576
Not only did he not go back to do his filial duty,

621
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:03,016
but he instead persuaded the family

622
00:26:03,040 --> 00:26:05,736
to wait for a few years.

623
00:26:05,760 --> 00:26:07,056
In the eyes of others,

624
00:26:07,080 --> 00:26:11,256
Chen Duxiu is a great hero of righteousness.

625
00:26:11,280 --> 00:26:12,696
But does anyone know,

626
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:15,256
that this is the great hero before you?

627
00:26:15,280 --> 00:26:17,856
He lived for himself

628
00:26:17,880 --> 00:26:21,776
and put the lives of his parents at risk.

629
00:26:21,800 --> 00:26:23,296
That's what's so treacherous.

630
00:26:23,320 --> 00:26:24,296
You shut up!

631
00:26:24,320 --> 00:26:25,136
Yannian!

632
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:28,240
You have wronged your father by saying so!

633
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:32,576
After the Second Revolution,

634
00:26:32,600 --> 00:26:35,256
Your father risked his life to persuade Gong Zhenpeng's troops in Wuhu

635
00:26:35,280 --> 00:26:38,456
to return to Anqing to fight Yuan.

636
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,536
However,

637
00:26:39,560 --> 00:26:41,576
this Gong Zhenpeng arrested your father.

638
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:43,916
The notice to be executed was posted.

639
00:26:43,940 --> 00:26:44,816
A matter of life and death,

640
00:26:44,840 --> 00:26:45,616
your father

641
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:48,320
didn't even frown!

642
00:26:48,360 --> 00:26:50,376
It was Liu Shuya who saved him later.

643
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:52,296
He died in Shanghai.

644
00:26:52,320 --> 00:26:54,576
He was the most wanted man at the time.

645
00:26:54,600 --> 00:26:57,016
A reward of one thousand yuan was offered.

646
00:26:57,040 --> 00:26:57,816
At that time,

647
00:26:57,840 --> 00:27:01,200
how could he possibly go back to Anqing?

648
00:27:04,280 --> 00:27:07,096
Yannian. Do you know

649
00:27:07,120 --> 00:27:09,896
the people who came to Shanghai to find your father?

650
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:12,536
They were sent by Ni Xichong.

651
00:27:12,560 --> 00:27:14,176
It was a trap!

652
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:16,776
Your father risked his life to return for a funeral

653
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:19,256
but we stopped him.

654
00:27:19,280 --> 00:27:20,496
He didn't go back.

655
00:27:20,520 --> 00:27:21,462
In those days,

656
00:27:21,486 --> 00:27:24,656
he pointed to the picture of Ni Xichong every day and said

657
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:27,336
he wanted to eat his own flesh!

658
00:27:27,360 --> 00:27:29,576
But what you said about your father

659
00:27:29,600 --> 00:27:30,736
is not fair to him.

660
00:27:30,760 --> 00:27:32,616
Then we were not wronged!

661
00:27:32,640 --> 00:27:33,640
My grandfather, my grandmother,

662
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:34,336
my mother, my cousin,

663
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:36,400
they were not wronged!

664
00:27:37,480 --> 00:27:40,096
Was he wronged? Was he aggrieved?

665
00:27:40,120 --> 00:27:42,376
It's not for us to judge.

666
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:43,656
Today, this matter

667
00:27:43,680 --> 00:27:45,376
is not a prank

668
00:27:45,400 --> 00:27:48,336
because he doesn't deserve to eat this dish.

669
00:27:48,360 --> 00:27:49,896
We did this today

670
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:52,496
as a way to explain to the family

671
00:27:52,520 --> 00:27:55,096
From now on, we clear our grudges,

672
00:27:55,120 --> 00:27:56,336
not cross each other's paths,

673
00:27:56,360 --> 00:27:57,976
and go our separate ways.

674
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:59,336
If you uncles and uncles feel

675
00:27:59,360 --> 00:28:01,536
that this is a prank

676
00:28:01,560 --> 00:28:03,856
then we apologise to everyone

677
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:06,080
for scaring our uncles and aunts.

678
00:28:13,080 --> 00:28:15,496
Aunt, we are sorry for your loss.

679
00:28:15,520 --> 00:28:16,936
We've scared you too.

680
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:18,456
It was not our intention.

681
00:28:18,480 --> 00:28:20,336
We don't hold a grudge against you.

682
00:28:20,360 --> 00:28:22,400
Please forgive us.

683
00:28:25,480 --> 00:28:26,671
Yannian!

684
00:28:26,695 --> 00:28:28,893
Yannian! Yannian!

685
00:28:32,920 --> 00:28:34,576
By the way,

686
00:28:34,600 --> 00:28:36,896
we didn't come to Shanghai to join you.

687
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:37,976
Let me put it to you this way,

688
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:38,616
we came

689
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:41,416
after we read the work-study initiative.

690
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:43,216
We decided to come to Shanghai to study French

691
00:28:43,240 --> 00:28:45,376
and go to France to work and study.

692
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:47,816
We'll make our own way,

693
00:28:47,840 --> 00:28:50,200
don't worry about it.

694
00:28:50,320 --> 00:28:52,216
Yannian! Qiaonian!

695
00:28:52,240 --> 00:28:54,256
Listen to me, Yannian!

696
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:57,040
This... I... I... you say, you say...

697
00:29:03,520 --> 00:29:06,336
Well, those are my sons.

698
00:29:06,360 --> 00:29:09,456
Zhong Fu, how can you laugh at that?

699
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:11,256
Both sons have disowned you.

700
00:29:11,280 --> 00:29:14,776
I, Chen Duxiu, have two such wonderful sons.

701
00:29:14,800 --> 00:29:17,360
Why can't I laugh?

702
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:19,496
I didn't get to give my parents a final send-off,

703
00:29:19,520 --> 00:29:21,416
I deserve to die for that.

704
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:22,736
The fact that they remembered to blame me

705
00:29:22,760 --> 00:29:25,116
shows that they are humane people.

706
00:29:25,140 --> 00:29:28,376
The fact that they are willing to work hard rather than rely on me

707
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:31,256
shows that they are self-reliant and self-sufficient people.

708
00:29:31,280 --> 00:29:33,456
In such a fragile world,

709
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:35,336
aren't these two qualities

710
00:29:35,360 --> 00:29:38,920
to be congratulated?

711
00:29:40,140 --> 00:29:42,976
Zhong Fu, you haven't said a word.

712
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:45,696
I'm still trying to figure out how to comfort you.

713
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:48,296
You, on the contrary, he's praising his son.

714
00:29:48,320 --> 00:29:49,616
But what he said,

715
00:29:49,640 --> 00:29:51,296
is a relief to us all.

716
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:51,967
It is.

717
00:29:51,967 --> 00:29:52,880
But Zhong Fu,

718
00:29:52,880 --> 00:29:55,336
I've just been watching your two boys,

719
00:29:55,360 --> 00:29:56,696
they're not normal.

720
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:58,464
They will be great men in the future.

721
00:29:58,488 --> 00:29:59,416
That's right!

722
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:02,840
These two children have high ambitions!

723
00:30:27,364 --> 00:30:28,816
Brother Mengzou.

724
00:30:28,840 --> 00:30:30,075
Apologies to you.

725
00:30:30,099 --> 00:30:31,976
You're not stingy

726
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:35,680
with your lotus leaf and yellow cow's trotters.

727
00:30:35,800 --> 00:30:37,736
I accept, I accept.

728
00:30:37,760 --> 00:30:38,576
Let's switch!

729
00:30:38,600 --> 00:30:39,496
You're dirty. You eat this.

730
00:30:39,520 --> 00:30:40,176
No, no, no.

731
00:30:40,200 --> 00:30:42,376
Didn't you hear what my son said?

732
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:44,680
I don't deserve to eat this dish.

733
00:30:45,040 --> 00:30:47,440
There are other dishes here.

734
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:48,862
So, so, so, let's do it!

735
00:30:48,886 --> 00:30:49,180
Come on!

736
00:30:49,180 --> 00:30:49,800
Come, come, come!

737
00:30:49,760 --> 00:30:50,336
Please, please!

738
00:30:50,360 --> 00:30:51,880
Have a drink!

739
00:30:54,920 --> 00:31:02,400
{\an8}[Waseda University dormitory, Japan]

740
00:31:05,653 --> 00:31:09,479
{\an8}[Li Dazhao, styled Shou Chang, student at Waseda University]

741
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:21,536
In 1915,

742
00:31:21,560 --> 00:31:23,496
the twenty-six-year-old Li Dazhao

743
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:27,056
wrote the article "Misanthropy and Self-awareness"

744
00:31:27,080 --> 00:31:30,376
against Chen Duxiu's "Patriotism and Self-consciousness",

745
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:32,200
as challenge.

746
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:34,736
With a positive and optimistic attitude,

747
00:31:34,760 --> 00:31:36,936
he urged the nation to rise

748
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:40,080
and join the movement against Yuan.

749
00:31:41,040 --> 00:31:42,776
Improving the spirit of nationalism

750
00:31:42,800 --> 00:31:46,536
and enouraging patriotism;

751
00:31:46,560 --> 00:31:48,456
by this time, Li Dazhao

752
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:49,816
had become

753
00:31:49,840 --> 00:31:53,840
a thoroughgoing anti-feudal activist.

754
00:32:11,655 --> 00:32:13,296
Shou Chang.

755
00:32:13,320 --> 00:32:15,016
What are you doing?

756
00:32:15,040 --> 00:32:17,323
You scared the hell out of me.

757
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:21,687
Mr. Xing Yan, what brings you here?

758
00:32:22,450 --> 00:32:23,010
Have a seat!

759
00:32:23,010 --> 00:32:25,680
I'm going back home, just wanted to see you.

760
00:32:26,120 --> 00:32:28,120
Please sit!

761
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:30,376
What's the matter? What's the panic?

762
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:32,320
Did something happen?

763
00:32:33,080 --> 00:32:34,044
I may have recently become

764
00:32:34,044 --> 00:32:36,016
a thorn in the side

765
00:32:36,040 --> 00:32:37,559
of some Japanese students.

766
00:32:37,559 --> 00:32:38,892
{\an8}[Zhang Tuzhao, styled Xing Yan, revolutionary exiled to Japan]

767
00:32:37,640 --> 00:32:39,696
They often use the pretext of supervising my classes

768
00:32:39,720 --> 00:32:40,816
to pick fights,

769
00:32:40,840 --> 00:32:41,896
destroying my manuscripts.

770
00:32:41,920 --> 00:32:43,536
So when I hear a knock at the door,

771
00:32:43,560 --> 00:32:46,240
my first thought was to hide the manuscript.

772
00:32:50,280 --> 00:32:52,856
You attend a variety of events and make a lot of appearances,

773
00:32:52,880 --> 00:32:55,440
it is inevitable that you will be watched.

774
00:32:56,200 --> 00:32:57,816
Shou Chang.

775
00:32:57,840 --> 00:33:00,840
I've heard the school has a lot to say about you.

776
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:03,976
Japanese universities are very strict in their administration.

777
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:04,896
You need to be careful.

778
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:06,654
{\an8}[Gan Yihao, student at Waseda University]

779
00:33:05,320 --> 00:33:05,976
You have to find

780
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:09,800
a way to make the most of both your studies and the revolution.

781
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:14,416
I heard you. I am organizing

782
00:33:14,440 --> 00:33:17,096
the Chinese Students Association in Japan.

783
00:33:17,120 --> 00:33:18,896
And I'm planning to talk to Yihan

784
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:20,856
to start a magazine called "Minyi" (Rule of people's will)

785
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:22,576
as a publication of the association.

786
00:33:22,600 --> 00:33:23,896
Inspired by the "Jiayin",

787
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:24,696
the "Minyi" also opposes

788
00:33:24,720 --> 00:33:26,576
and resists Yuan Shikai's authoritarian politics

789
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:29,416
by commenting and discussing the current situation,

790
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:30,856
to foster a modern civilization

791
00:33:30,880 --> 00:33:32,496
and promote the awakening of the people.

792
00:33:32,520 --> 00:33:34,696
It did make me miss a lot of classes,

793
00:33:34,720 --> 00:33:35,856
but the revolutionary situation at the moment

794
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:37,256
is in full swing.

795
00:33:37,280 --> 00:33:39,056
I had a really hard time choosing.

796
00:33:39,080 --> 00:33:40,298
This is not acceptable.

797
00:33:40,322 --> 00:33:41,296
In my opinion,

798
00:33:41,320 --> 00:33:43,856
academics are also the essence of the revolution.

799
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:45,336
Now that you are in the door,

800
00:33:45,360 --> 00:33:47,016
you must get your diploma.

801
00:33:47,040 --> 00:33:48,216
Otherwise, it'll be a shame.

802
00:33:48,240 --> 00:33:52,456
In fact, the usual is doing quite well.

803
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:53,456
In 11 subjects last school year,

804
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:55,376
he scored 736 points.

805
00:33:55,400 --> 00:33:56,696
In politics and economics,

806
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:57,816
out of 106 students

807
00:33:57,840 --> 00:33:59,976
he ranked in the top 40.

808
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:01,736
Because he's never had a high school education

809
00:34:01,760 --> 00:34:03,336
and went straight to undergraduate school,

810
00:34:03,360 --> 00:34:06,216
that's a good grade, it's not bad.

811
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:08,616
Just third place, it's a shame.

812
00:34:08,640 --> 00:34:10,296
Third place is really not bad.

813
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:11,696
You're good and you're willing to work hard.

814
00:34:11,720 --> 00:34:13,456
Academics are not a problem for you.

815
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:16,080
Compliance with school rules is your problem.

816
00:34:17,600 --> 00:34:19,136
I'm really at a bit of a loss now.

817
00:34:19,160 --> 00:34:22,376
What is more important, the revolution or school?

818
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:25,080
It's really hard for me to choose.

819
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:26,656
You put yourself out on a hot day,

820
00:34:26,680 --> 00:34:28,816
